      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat the reserved pan with a very generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> (enough to cover the bottom of the pan!) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> breaded chicken</strong> and cook for 5-6 min on each side or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the outside is golden</p><p>On a clean board, slice the <strong>breaded</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> finely into strips – this is your <strong>chicken katsu</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1687441298672-x200.jpg",
