            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build your buns, fill each <strong>bao bun</strong> with the<strong> chicken katsu</strong> and top with some of the <strong>katsu sauce </strong>– these are your<strong> chicken katsu bao buns</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chicken katsu bao buns </strong>with the <strong>furikake rice</strong>, <strong>quick-pickled cucumber </strong>and any <strong>remaining katsu sauce </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish the<strong> </strong>rice<strong> </strong>with the <strong>reserved toasted sesame seeds </strong>and<strong> seaweed flakes</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
